flowchart TB
    Client([Client])
    UploadURL[Pre-signed URL Service]
    ObjectStore[(Object Store<br/>raw + variants)]
    Processor[Image Processor<br/>thumb / small / med / full]
    CDN[(CDN<br/>edge cache)]
    PostSvc[Post Service<br/>metadata + fan-out]
    MetaDB[(Posts Metadata<br/>wide-column,<br/>partition by user)]
    FeedSvc[Feed Service<br/>hybrid push/pull + rank]

    Client -->|request URL| UploadURL
    Client -->|PUT media| ObjectStore
    ObjectStore -.->|event trigger| Processor
    Processor --> ObjectStore
    Processor --> CDN
    Processor -.->|notify| PostSvc
    PostSvc --> MetaDB
    Client -->|read feed| FeedSvc
    FeedSvc --> MetaDB
    FeedSvc -->|signed URLs| CDN
    CDN -->|media| Client

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class UploadURL,Processor,PostSvc,FeedSvc service
    class ObjectStore,CDN,MetaDB store
